# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# combined — __iter__, __next__, __len__ across all 5 pathlib subjects
#
# 5 classes x 3 methods = 15 rows.
# All fifteen values are false; no pathlib class implements the iterator
# or sequence length protocols in its own __dict__.
# Path objects are immutable filesystem path value types; the iterator
# protocol (__iter__, __next__) and length protocol (__len__) are not
# part of the pathlib API.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

